mployed builder � this service handles the enquiries your business actually receives. That covers every building specialisation: house extensions (single and double storey), loft conversions, garage conversions, new builds, renovations and refurbishments, structural alterations, groundworks and foundations, brickwork and blockwork, underpinning, basement conversions, barn conversions, commercial fit-outs, shop fitting, property development, demolition, and insurance reinstatement work. Whether you're pricing domestic kitchen extensions or managing multi-unit residential developments, the AI captures enquiries at the level of detail your business requires." },
